{"tid":2487440,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"輕小說-ダンジョンに出会いを求めるのは間違っているだろうか 17卷","createTime":"2021-04-13T14:09:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T07:12:15.000Z","uid":7307,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"3af41f147af200c3924f10af2e4ff531e6e9ecdc","tid":2487440,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T14:09:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeMhg67y5yzANr2XUwB3i5SEL4rjKUncLQ3MeQyuRnEqQ?filename=G6Wv8Jx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG6Wv8Jx.jpg&h=c70f3158&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZ9JXz6tt7sjybfphHUrB3t8SiTpPoWJcvNfToqp8xwtr?filename=pswHfoy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpswHfoy.jpg&h=688a37ff&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfECPw6qbmepZ6PC8Sokgr2QrT8SB3rq8uA3oybCwRJp9?filename=UAUNrve.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUAUNrve.jpg&h=5fe507d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n序章弗雷雅獨白，順便解釋了能鑽漏洞變身希兒是因為赫倫的魔法跟交換真名的關係，<br />\n希兒這外貌和身分是原本在天界就常用的偽裝。<br />\n<br />\n一章接著16卷最後，貝爾打槍希兒後跟大家會合，貝爾內疚的不敢面對艾絲。<br />\n隔天琉過來找貝爾，貝爾直接攤牌被希兒告白後拒絕她了，<br />\n因為有憧憬的對象所以不能接受希兒的心意，琉聽完恍然大悟，<br />\n然後兩人一起出門尋找希兒。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面赫斯提亞在街上馬上遇到弗雷雅來賭人，弗雷雅直接攤牌她要搶人，<br />\n這踩到赫斯提亞的底線所以直接拒絕，然後弗雷雅就下令當場開戰，<br />\n雖然赫米斯有下令眷族要看好弗雷雅眷族，愛伊夏也有因為春姬要被攻擊而直接介入，<br />\n不過還是一瞬間偉爾夫、命、莉莉、春姬就被矮人四兄弟和艾倫打趴。<br />\n試閱就到莉莉拔出魔劍應戰不敵被打暈結束。"},{"pid":"33fa3a95443737bdc4ea04bc15c62b9deb0b1562","tid":2487440,"uid":50935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T15:40:55.000Z","msg":"高Lv打低lv 人又多 又玩偷襲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44550d5624dfafebb7445626837ae186cf8bea62","tid":2487440,"uid":72590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T15:42:21.000Z","msg":"試讀<br />\n<a href=\"http://ul.sbcr.jp/GA-mg0fO\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ful.sbcr.jp%2FGA-mg0fO&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11MdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=ca549e9f\" target=\"_blank\">http://ul.sbcr.jp/GA-mg0fO</a>"},{"pid":"0a045c3c19bb71c61d042bae1c460107d55ab21b","tid":2487440,"uid":222966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T17:13:00.000Z","msg":"琉同亞絲菲並肩作戰型到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一開始就俾人打暈晒，咁就點打？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />完全諗唔到點贏，除非洛基幫手，不過我估佢食花生多d"},{"pid":"225644b1bae7217c3aeb8672c18778d0f660f145","tid":2487440,"uid":209097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33fa3a95443737bdc4ea04bc15c62b9deb0b1562","tid":2487440,"uid":50935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T15:40:55.000Z","msg":"高Lv打低lv 人又多 又玩偷襲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T17:17:58.000Z","msg":"成個眷族突然間cheap曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a885c12d4d9ad4427f734908ee697065b331f8c","tid":2487440,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"225644b1bae7217c3aeb8672c18778d0f660f145","tid":2487440,"uid":209097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33fa3a95443737bdc4ea04bc15c62b9deb0b1562","tid":2487440,"uid":50935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T15:40:55.000Z","msg":"高Lv打低lv 人又多 又玩偷襲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T17:17:58.000Z","msg":"成個眷族突然間cheap曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T22:01:49.000Z","msg":"本身都唔係頂班"},{"pid":"fdd6e5ddcf8ada11d77751df658a9db64adc7dec","tid":2487440,"uid":50935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a885c12d4d9ad4427f734908ee697065b331f8c","tid":2487440,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"225644b1bae7217c3aeb8672c18778d0f660f145","tid":2487440,"uid":209097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco